does it provide ends. It is preeminently a means to serve what we
think is right.'' In two recent decisions _ one involving prize
fighter Mike Tyson, the other a wild police party _ a New York
court did the right thing. By DAN LYNCH.
</P>
<P>
   FLORES-COLUMN (San Antonio) _ I've never understood why men's
groups have bashed the annual Take Our Daughters To Work Day. What
about boys, the men's advocates say? Spare me. Is it not enough
that women in corporate America hold only 2 percent of executive
positions, yet make up 46 percent of the workforce? Seems to me,
boys are getting along just fine. By VERONICA FLORES.
</P>
