   CALIF-EGYPTIAN-THEATER (Hollywood) _ Hollywood's oldtime glamour
is epitomized by the Egyptian theater, which is to be restored. By
Todd S. Purdum.
</P>
<P>
   SALVADOR-DALTON (San Salvador, El Salvador) _ Arts Abroad: Roque
Dalton, revolutionary and writer, becomes respectable in San
Salvador 25 years after his death. By Larry Rohter.
</P>
<P>
   TONYS (New York) _ Broadway developments in the wake of the Tony
Awards. By Rick Lyman.
</P>
