   SCI-COMPUTER-COLUMN (Undated) _ Viewpoint Datalabs International
Inc. has helped create many computer-generated models for
television and the movies, including the latest version of
``Godzilla.'' Liveart98, its first product for the general public,
trades the monsters for bugs. When it works it is hard to beat, but
it does not work that often. By Stephen Manes.
</P>
