<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-08 16:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9352 &Cx1f; gen-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-STATES-BUDGETTHISISTH     06-08 0340
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-STATES-BUDGET </SLUG>
  THIS IS THE STATES NEWS SERVICE BUDGET FOR JUNE
8, 1998. IF YOU HAVE ANY QUESTIONS, PLEASE CALL US AT 202-628-3100.
<TEXT>
<P>
   GEORGIA -- PARCA. Frustrated by a lack of movement on his
managed-care reform bill, U.S. Rep. Charlie Norwood is calling for
the ouster of a fellow Republican from the House panel working on
the issue. Williams
</P>
<P>
   -- COVER. U.S. Sen. Paul Coverdell, R-Ga., is holding a news
