<P>
   ISRAEL-JUDIASM _ JERUSALEM _ Standing behind police barricades
at the holy site of the Western Wall, American leaders in the
less-traditional, Reform, branch of Judaism Monday said Israel is
trying to de-legitimize them. Eric Yoffie, president of the Union
of American Hebrew Congregations and about 100 rabbis and members
of Reform congregations are attempting to dissuade Israeli leaders
from passing the so-called Conversion Law. (Kaplow, Cox News
Service). EDs: To move by 2 p.m. ET.
</P>
