   NATIONAL
</P>
<P>
   TEXAS-DROUGHT _ AUSTIN, Texas (developing) Wildfire experts who
have been assessing dry conditions in Central Texas will identify
some of the most serious problems Monday, while Texas Gov. George
W. Bush is expected to address the drought in a press conference.
He may be asking for federal assistance to fight wildfires.
(Banta/Herman, Austin American-Statesman)
</P>
