<DOCNO> NYT19980608.0217 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-08 17:19 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9479 &Cx1f; tdt-z
