graduates with engineering degrees are smiling? Because they are
being offered big bucks by employers. Jobtrak Corp., which operates
an online job-listing site that links employers, universities and
students, said a May survey of selected schools nationwide found
that engineering graduates were being offered an average starting
salary of $58,513, the highest of 24 careers measured by the
survey. (Tharpe, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
